post_content:
Finished my 2nd t206 set and really only need one so I just listed on ebay.  

It's a 520 that has every card a PSA 2 with no qualifiers or half grades.  I think it represents pretty well for the grade with a few clunkers for the gradej(as you might expect).

Here's the link:

[url]https://www.ebay.com/itm/175887133707[/url]

For the set registry which has all of the images, click here:

[url]https://www.psacard.com/psasetregistry/baseball/t206-sets/1909-11-t206-complete-player-image-set-no-wagner-doyle-n-y-natl-plank-magie/publishedset/390557[/url]

Please PM if you have any questions but please don't ask if I'm breaking the set or what's the best I can do.  Price is shown on the ebay listing so feel free to make an offer if you'd like.  

Happy to meet in person to do an exchange as well provided it's within a reasonable distance from Central Ohio.  

Thanks and yes, I'm keeping my other set....haha

Troy Rambo

I've had a few people inquire about trades in part or full.  I'm likely not interested in trading in full as it would probably require too many cards to even it out.  If you do have something you'd like to put together, do let me know, though.  I'm open to it.  

Thanks!

Sorry to bump this to the top but I've had a few PMs lately about the set so I thought I'd let people know the set is no longer available.

Thanks for your interest and questions!
Excellent.  Congrats, Troy!  When will you start a 3rd 520??:D

Ha!  thanks!  No plans to do another 520.  I'll keep the big set (522) and work on a few upgrades but will likely focus on some other tobacco era sets.  Especially now that I have some extra room w/the 2 set being gone!  

Then again, maybe a binder set???.... hmmm.....
